---
title: Lamb Shoulder Korma & Garlic Greens with Rice, Yoghurt & Coriander
description: Indulge in culinary excellence with this dish that’s sure to dazzle! For tonight’s dinner, we’ve done the hard bit for you by
slow-cooking this lamb shoulder to meltingly tender perfection. Shredded and stirred through a delicious korma sauce, we just
know you’ll love this one!
